No. 29,

Misc.

Moore v. Michigan. Petitioner pro se. Thomas M. Kavanagh, Attorney General *908of Michigan, Edmund E. Shepherd, Solicitor General, and Daniel J. O’Hara, Assistant Attorney General, for respondent.

*907Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis and petition for writ of cer-tiorari to the Supreme Court of Michigan granted.
